Add new event to `SessionStoreEvents`:
```typescript
'permission-request': [pending: PendingPermission, resolve: (optionId: string | null) => void];
'permission-mode-changed': [mode: 'auto' | 'ask'];
```

Add `permissionMode` state to `SessionStore`:
```typescript
permissionMode: 'auto' | 'ask' = 'auto';
setPermissionMode(mode: 'auto' | 'ask') { ... }
```

